  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emotional intelligence classes for 30 kids under 8</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The depression and suicide rates among children has increased 200% in the past years. One of the main reasons is the lack of emotional intelligence due to over exposure to digital electronics and absent parents. To lower the statistics, we offer a space where kids can learn to identify and channel their emotions with yoga, painting, crafts, singing and meditation. Through weekly classes for three hours, the kids are exposed to a different way of learning about emotions in a safe environment.</narrative>
  </description>
